    <section>
        <h2>Technical Infrastructure</h2>
        <p>DRUW is built on <a href="http://hyr.ax">Samvera Hyrax</a>, an open source technology. Our data model is PCDM. DRUW will accept any file format. However, please refer to the <%= link_to 'what can be deposited', main_app.faq_path%> section of the FAQ for a list of suggested formats.
        </p>
    </section>

